# Task-ecomm 

This is a simple backend API for an eCommerce system built using ExpressJS, MongoDB, and JWT for authentication.

## Features
- User registration and login with JWT-based authentication
- CRUD operations for products (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
- JWT-protected routes for adding, updating, and deleting products

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/ecommerce-api.git

 ### folder structure

